name: cytokinesis
description: Imitation is flattery, but reproducing perfection is divine.

name: gaffar's peace pipe
description: Now now, no need to run off and spoil a perfectly good day. Have a seat. You remind me of someone I met long ago. I don't know, could have been 12, no 15, years ago now. It was in the Autumn, and what a harvest it was that year...

name: synchronicity
description: I can always feel my brothers and sisters. Their thoughts are mine. Their feelings are mine. Their intent is mine. We may be many, but we act as one.

name: recon
description: Even the smallest blade can be deadly if you know where and how to strike.

name: ashes to ashes
description: What we become, is what we came from.

name: graphene batteries
description: They are more of a slow release explosion than a battery. Comprised of highly volatile chemicals, it has a singular cycle life and outputs immense amounts of energy. Handle with fear lest we all feel the catastrophic consequences.

name: kethtrexamine
description: The battle raged on, but we didn't lose an inch of ground. Our Keth kept us going but who knows what the long term side effects are. Very dangerous over short distances.

name: orbital strike
description: The clouds opened and for a moment they expected the warmth of the sun. Instead, they felt the fury of the Marcolian High Guard.

name: neutron bomb
description: When negotiation fails, the Marcolian simply wipe the slate clean, and build in their image.

name: artillery volley
description: We fired from the safety of the walls and watched the garish brutes flee. They underestimated Marcolian artillery.

name: revitalizing growth
description: The breath of life flows through the Earthen, giving them strength to stand once again and defend their home.

name: archivist's pride
description: Our sequences are retained and so too, we hope, our souls.

description: Antius was amongst the best of us. Perhaps, with this opportunity, you shall be too.

name: reliant gamma
description: Kathari are the tide. They flow as one. Together, there is no single barrier that can stop them.

name: foundry technician
description: The foundry-ships of the Augencore never cease their productions, the great furnaces at their core powering ship & industry alike.

name: repurposed hardware
description: Those first years on Mars would have been the death of us, but our ingenuity and resourcefulness kept us alive. Now it will be our enemies' downfall.

name: collateral damage
description: Try as we might, there will always be unwanted casualties of war. Ideally, more for them than for us.

name: change of heart
description: Look around and see what we are fighting over. We feel it and we can control it, and you are now a part of it. Violence and anger are a stain upon this vista. Find your calm and lower your weapon. Be at peace.

name: ocular implant
description: Never play an Augencore Warrior in a game of Poker.

name: life well
description: Not all that awaits explorers of deep space is horrifying. Much of what is waiting to be discovered is, in human terms, quite miraculous. Tonight we bathe in the cosmos itself.

name: entropy's reach
description: Immobilizing. Debilitating. Few can resist.

name: genetic correction
description: All will benefit from the advances of Kathari Bio-Science. Whether they are willing is another matter.

name: demolecularize
description: The Shroud often leave behind no trace of their victims, no evidence, no clue as to their goals. Entire ships, gone in the blink of an eye.

name: supply drop
description: “The good news, HQ has dropped fresh rounds & rations for us. The bad news, they’ve landed about 3 kilometres into bandit territory.” - Unknown Marcolian Sergeant

name: strength of mars
description: More than one Marcolian has overcome adversity by seeing the flag of Mars fly high across the Battlefield. You will be no different.

name: enthalpy's grasp
description: Crushing. Overwhelming. Few can resist.

name: marcolian bannerman
description: The Banner of Mars flies high amongst the Marcolian forces. The act of carrying it is a great honour, often awarded to those who have shown great courage in past conflicts, as it is to be guarded with their life.

name: malachite shield
description: “We protect our planet, and in return, the very Earth itself rises to protect us.” - Soliea, Disciple of Gaffar

name: galaxy key
description: Look to the stars, look beyond what's there. A constellation aligned the way is clear.
